erkommunene og deres kommunale bedrifter.", "Selskapet eies av Trondheim samt kommunene G\u00e4vle, Sundsvall, Kiruna, Pite\u00e5, Uppsala, Trollh\u00e4ttan, Helsingborg, \u00d6rnsk\u00f6ldsvik og Ume\u00e5."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "6e927c8492b0c697ff22ea8a1e295437b6bbc279e1cacc2ddabff2a3ac9755da"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-03-08T12:23:24.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "- Det ser ut til \u00e5 v\u00e6re en alvorlig sak, sier Ellen Reitan, nestleder i kontrollkomiteen i Trondheim."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article14409667.ece/wg7l1a/ALTERNATES/w980-default/To%20rom%20og%20kjokken.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/bd4d0e9d38b77daeeb0ae7b572bd9e251e5f362c.jpg?58f8869b"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Dette vil de vite om de kommuneansattes pengebruk -adressa.no", "156 000 kroner", "Ubesvarte sp\u00f8rsm\u00e5l", "- Mandatet v\u00e5rt", "S\u00e6rlig dyrt i Trondheim"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "bd4d0e9d38b77daeeb0ae7b572bd9e251e5f362c"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["Trondheim kommune", "alkohol", "Sverige", "Olaf L\u00f8berg"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Trondheim kommune,alkohol,Sverige,Olaf L\u00f8berg"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "law-government-and-politics"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["s\u00e6rlig dyr", "kommune", "personen jobber", "kommuneansattes pengebruk", "alvorlig sak", "kommune knyttes", "private konsulenter", "sak", "mandatet v\u00e5rt"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["trondheim og oslo", "arbetarbladet", "adresseavisen", "ernst", "svenska kommun f\u00f6rs\u00e4krings ab"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["young", "sverige", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-